 <p><lb/>Anno 1597 <foreign xml:lang="en">the 29 <choice><orig>I</orig><reg>J</reg></choice>aniari <lb/><choice><orig>♄</orig><reg type="gloss">Saturday</reg></choice> <choice><orig>An’ m’</orig><reg>am</reg></choice> at 45 <choice><orig>p</orig><reg>post</reg><reg type="gloss">past</reg></choice> 3.</foreign> in <choice><orig>q<hi rend="superscript">o</hi></orig><reg>quo</reg></choice> <lb/>tem<choice><orig><g ref="#crossedp"></g></orig><reg type="normalisation">por</reg></choice>e somnat<choice><orig>ꝯ</orig><reg>us</reg></choice> sum De A Y <lb/>Scire quomodo sec<choice><orig>ū</orig><reg>um</reg></choice> stat, an <lb/>sit aut erit vidua et qu<choice><orig>ā</orig><reg>an</reg></choice>do <lb/>et qua mens mihi gerit &amp;c/</p>
