<div xml:id="translation001" xml:lang="en" decls="#translation">
<p>Saturday 29 January in the year 1597 at 45 past 3, at which time I dreamed of A Y. To know how things stand with her, whether she is or will be a widow and when, and how she feels about me etc.</p>
